verbose_text: We found that while systemic delivery of mATF-IONPs or ScFvEGFR-IONPs induced the production of the high levels of anti-mATF or anti-ScFvEGFR antibodies, the mice that received the same amount and dose schedule of mATF-IONP-Dox and ScFvEGFR-IONP-Dox had significantly lower levels of the anti-targeting ligand antibodies.
evidence: amount and dose schedule of mATF-IONP-Dox and ScFvEGFR-IONP-Dox
